{"tid":2141130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安樂排污滿瀉傳惡臭  泵回管道直出白海豚棲息地","createTime":"2020-08-05T12:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T21:17:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80cc55d510cef1171cdd3833530e47f06323ca53","tid":2141130,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/ITKSBTXLKKFM7UFSOEMUBIUPUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FITKSBTXLKKFM7UFSOEMUBIUPUE%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=cb7e9923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FITKSBTXLKKFM7UFSOEMUBIUPUE%2F&h=ba645d0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/ITKSBTXLKKFM7UFSOEMUBIUPUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n安樂排污滿瀉傳惡臭 <br />\n泵回管道直出白海豚棲息地<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司司長鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶旗下的上市公司安樂工程又爆風波。本報收到投訴，指該公司有份承建的新圍污水處理廠6月底測試期間，有污水溢流到測試範圍外，投訴人質疑污水未經處理即排走造成污染。渠務署承認部份排放水可能溢流至未啟用的設施，但稱承建商已安排泵機將排放水泵回預設管道，強調排放水水質符合標準，指有關情況屬預計內。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：新系統垃圾隔濾率跌八成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G6ql22WdmDpndOLx9PVazUBuWYM=/640x608/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MRPJHVD2I2A7O3FPCA4JC4XP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG6ql22WdmDpndOLx9PVazUBuWYM%3D%2F640x608%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MRPJHVD2I2A7O3FPCA4JC4XP4.jpg&h=c4f064cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排放水溢流至處理廠測試範圍外的水井，水質混濁兼夾雜垃圾。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n有不願具名投訴人透露，新圍污水處理廠6月26至30日測試污水處理系統，其間有污水湧到測試範圍區域外，廠房最後動用水泵、泵車吸走污水；。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p_iIlG5HKBV2PJnSFa1M7yy9Gkc=/466x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2NSUAHXVSOD6O7SLBSGTFLJEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp_iIlG5HKBV2PJnSFa1M7yy9Gkc%3D%2F466x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2NSUAHXVSOD6O7SLBSGTFLJEQ.jpg&h=de9006c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潘樂陶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渠務署曾頒「整潔大獎」<br />\n<br />\n2016年安樂工程與得利滿、中國港灣聯營承建元朗新圍污水處理廠改善工程，項目總造價25.7億元，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教大科學與環境學系副教授曾耀輝指，排放水指已處理污水，若溢流至廠房未啟用設施，影響相對輕微，但若是溢流至廠房以外地方或雨水渠，或違反《水污染管制條例》，現階段難判斷溢流原因。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n渠務署解釋水井中的雜物。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e9a5b66a156588440bf65a8c9d0f1d861702d311","tid":2141130,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670493d844b001dfef86ce9d0f7ecc65968b6d08","tid":2141130,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"冇事既 佢地有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d5723b7ec826b52e4a9235ff7fe413d5648c59","tid":2141130,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c1b3b4beb388f93d51da8324c950ffb871818b","tid":2141130,"uid":345819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T21:17:25.000Z","msg":"將啲污水裝返落大波驊對波畀佢老公飲"}]}